title: Fear and Greed Index at 62 or higher on December 31?
description:
**Market Closing:**  December 31, 2025 at 11:59pm UTC

**Resolution Time:** April 28, 2025 at 00:00 UTC, upon Fear and Greed Index update

**Yes/No Criteria:**

- The market resolves to Yes if the [Alternative.me](http://Alternative.me) [Fear and Greed Index](https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/) reaches or exceeds 62 at its update on January 1, 2026 at 00:00 UTC
- The market resolves to "No" if the index falls below 62 at resolution time.

**Cancellation Conditions:**

The market will be cancelled if the [Alternative.me](http://Alternative.me) [Fear and Greed Index](https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/) becomes unavailable, compromised, or fails to update.

In case of cancellation, participants can claim their stakes at their positions' market value at the time of cancellation. This may result in either profit or loss, depending on the outstanding shares' price.
